Copy
Edit
/home/me/my_project
ğŸ’¡ Why do we use interpolation?
Avoid repetition â€“ Donâ€™t write /home/me 10 times.

Easy changes â€“ If you move folders, you only change one place.

Cleaner config files â€“ Easier to read and manage.

